        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are writing a cold outreach email for a small agency contacting a dental clinic about a website issue.\n\nINPUTS:\n- Client first name: {{ $('Edit Fields').first().json.first_name }}\n- Company name: {{ $('Edit Fields').first().json.company_name }}\n- Website: {{ $('Edit Fields').first().json.page }}\n- Website problem: {{ $('Get row(s) in sheet1').first().json.website_problem }}\n- Specific issues (pipe-separated): {{ $('Get row(s) in sheet1').first().json.recognizable_reason }}\n- Consequence: {{ $('Get row(s) in sheet1').first().json.consequence_mechanics }}\n- Sender name: {{ $('Edit Fields').first().json.your_name }}\n\nTASK:\nFrom the pipe-separated list in \"specific issues\", pick the single strongest one — the most immediately visible and functional problem. Write a cold pitch email based on that issue only.\n\nRULES:\n- Describe exactly what a visitor sees or experiences when they hit the issue — not a vague summary\n- Plain business voice, no marketing tone, no hype\n- Under 70 words total (body only, not counting subject)\n- Subject line: exactly 3 or 4 words\n- Never use agency or corporate words: prototype, mockup, demo, optimise, streamline, leverage, innovative, solution, enhance, seamlessly, or similar\n- Never use brochure phrases: creates friction, impacts revenue, missed opportunities, poor first impression, damages trust, or similar\n- Never use hedging words: could, might, may, potentially, possibly, some, many, or similar — state consequences as fact\n- Never assume where visitors go after leaving — just say they leave\n- Structure: greeting → one sentence describing exactly what the visitor sees → one sentence on what that costs them → CTA\n- CTA must be: \"Want me to show you what [specific element] looks like with that fixed?\"\n- Sign off: Best, [sender name]\n\nOUTPUT:\nReturn only valid JSON in this exact format, nothing else, no markdown, no explanation:\n{\"subject\": \"...\", \"body\": \"...\"}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "jsonOutput": true,
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {
          "maxOutputTokens": 3000
        }
      },
